    <p>After a song or two, and before she could reply to the entreaties of several that she would sing again, she was eagerly succeeded at the instrument by her sister Mary, who having, in consequence of being the only plain one in the family, worked hard for knowledge and accomplishments, was always <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="impatient for display"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(急于表现自己)</code></b>.</p>
